_sText:
This is freefalltohell.  It's from counter-strike 1.6 and i thought i would make it for Counter Strike: Source.
Start of round, shoot the glass under the players and fall down the map to land on many square that will teleport you
to a ledge with weapons on them. last man standing wins the round for their team.
This is one the first version and i will think of ways to improve it.

Thanks, Slippers
